snippet.title: 'Neath the Neon Star - Terraria: The Stars Above 2.1 Trailer
snippet.description:
The Neon Veil awaits...
https://discord.gg/starsabove | Join the Discord today!

With tons of new weapons, new Stellar Nova upgrades, new dialogue with voice acting, new foes to fight, and a brand new biome in the main world, 'Neath the Neon Star is the largest update to The Stars Above yet!

Featuring voice work from the talented Kiera Rhodes- voicing both of the Starfarers!
Additionally featuring one of the new Stars Above original tracks, "Analog Memory" composed by Yuda Prasetia N!
